name: WAY OUT
description: I took this image a while a go but haven't thought much, or edited, but at some point I just started editing it for hours and ended up with this. My days were pretty terrible for last few days, because of working too hard, having self doubts, emotional low points and etc. I think those emotions reflected on this photo, and editing. Now I believe there's a way out. Way out of this endless dark tunnel. / Format : JPEG / Image size : 5517 × 2982
